#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_s1
msgid ""
"Actions address material workforce impacts such as labor conditions,\n"
"                                diversity,\n"
"                                inclusion, health &amp; safety, training, "
"and social dialogue.\n"
"                                Resources are\n"
"                                allocated to mitigate risks, enhance "
"positive impacts, and implement\n"
"                                workforce-related programs. Actions are "
"prioritized based on\n"
"                                severity and likelihood\n"
"                                of impacts, following a mitigation "
"hierarchy: prevent, reduce,\n"
"                                remediate, promote\n"
"                                positive opportunities. Engagement with "
"workers and representatives\n"
"                                informs the\n"
"                                planning and execution of actions."
msgstr ""
"Las acciones abordan impactos materiales en la fuerza laboral como "
"condiciones laborales,\n"
"                            diversidad,\n"
"                            inclusión, salud y seguridad, capacitación y "
"diálogo social.\n"
"                            Asignan recursos para mitigar riesgos, potenciar "
"impactos positivos e implementar\n"
"                            programas relacionados con la fuerza laboral. "
"Priorizan acciones según\n"
"                            la gravedad y la probabilidad\n"
"                            de los impactos, con una jerarquía de "
"mitigación: prevenir, reducir,\n"
"                            remediar, promover\n"
"                            oportunidades positivas. La participación de los "
"trabajadores y representantes\n"
"                            sirve para la\n"
"                            planificación y ejecución de las acciones."

