"                                        datos estén desglosados \n"
"                                        y cubran todos los aspectos "
"materiales."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_g1
msgid ""
"Disclosure\n"
"                                        includes lobbying expenditures, "
"memberships, and\n"
"                                        engagement in policy or regulatory "
