"Workforce data are reviewed internally by sustainability and HR "
"specialists.\n"
"                For high-risk suppliers or regions, third-party assurance is "
"performed under\n"
"                recognized standards, such as SA8000 or ISO 45001."
msgstr ""
"Los datos del personal los revisan especialistas de sostenibilidad y RR. HH. "
"de forma interna.\n"
"                Para proveedores o regiones de alto riesgo, se lleva a cabo "
"una verificación con terceros\n"
"                bajo estándares reconocidos, como SA8000 o ISO 45001."

